   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     Removed/updated obsoleted <command>ceph-disk</command> occurrences
     (Fate#324466).
    </para>
   </listitem>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     Added <xref linkend="cephfs-quotas" /> (Fate#323422).
